metadata.name: Reflections
metadata.description:
The art of self-portrait is self-expression, exploring one's feelings and emotions through art. This is a very powerful way of expressing one's self and expressing one's emotions to others.  

The self-portrait journey was a way for me to express my artistic experimentation, and a way to share my creativity and vision explorations. I invite you into this photographic journey. My hope is that you enjoy the journey as much as I enjoyed experimenting!
